              },
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 2,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "“As the U.S. withdrawal approached, analysts thought it would be months before the Taliban brought the fight to Kabul. This is the story of why it happened and what came after — by a reporter and photographer who witnessed it all.”",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
